{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef5dc85fec","title":"野战军应开至西峰镇","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f1200022a","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":14,"articleId":"ef5dc85fec"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"57cdc77007","type":"paragraph","text":"野战军应开至西峰镇","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"},{"id":"99100a5afa","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月14日）彭、任”","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"},{"id":"f079cdbd8d","type":"paragraph","text":"野战军应开至西峰镇。有如下理由甲、南京已发动大规模内战，全力对付张杨，主力由潼关进","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"},{"id":"75ceeaceba","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、张杨内部有许多不稳成分，南京政策又拉杨打张，红军与之靠拢，壮其胆而振其气","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"},{"id":"3be6c6b4ce","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、靠近张杨，可应付各种事变，远离则不能。丁、西峰镇靠近王以哲，仍可打胡成、不管西安能守与否，南下有几种机动。已、暂时出宁夏不可能，且变为单独的。张杨同时则进入溢路。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"},{"id":"97aa580727","type":"paragraph","text":"庚、在现地暂时不动，无付可打，对张杨危急又不能救。依上理由，所以第一步到西峰镇","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"},{"id":"550b66481e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"},{"id":"5ae09c2b0a","type":"paragraph","text":"十四日[1]彭、任，指彭德怀、任强时，当时分别任红军前敌总指挥和政治委员。21西峰镇，即今甘肃西峰市。[3]张杨，指张学良和杨虎城。141王以哲，当时任国民党军东北军第六十七军军长。15]胡，指胡宗南，当时任国民党军第一军军长兼第一师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec"}],"page":{"id":"e9e401b415","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"ef5dc85fec","start":166,"end":166}}}},"__N_SSG":true}